name: PIB
description:
PIB (PB) is an experimental token in the construction of decentralized community. PIB protocol is based on the token issued by coin an intelligent ecological chain.
The first decentralized Oracle network that allows anyone to securely provide smart contracts, access critical external data, offline payments, and any other API functionality. Any user with a data feed, offline service (such as local payment) or any other API can offer it directly to a smart contract in exchange for a BNB token.
